      <title>警方称 Novo 火灾与天气和吸烟有关，而非犯罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/police-cite-weather-smoking-rather-than-crime-in-novo-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[警方没有发现与诺和诺德公司丹麦制造中心火灾相关的犯罪活动的迹象，称天气和吸烟等因素可能是造成 5 月份火灾的原因。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/police-cite-weather-smoking-rather-than-crime-in-novo-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 08:51:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
